what_failed: Regression (0.37x): Created a filtered_items CTE to push item filters early, simplified the overlapping price range, converted implicit joins to explicit JOIN syntax, created cross_sales_base to isolate the fact table joins with store/returns/customer, and pushed year filters into the cross_sales CTE to reduce aggregation size.
why_it_failed: Created both filtered (store_sales_agg, web_sales_agg) AND original (ss, ws) versions of the same aggregations. The query does a 6-way self-join matching quarterly patterns (Q1->Q2->Q3). Duplicate CTEs doubled materialization and confused the optimizer's cardinality estimates for the multi-self-join.
